channel.title: [PI] DutchReality - Can you escape the dangers? [PI]
channel.description:
Hey guys, I was working on this project untill we stopped because of school :/ So I thought: "Why not releasing it?" Here it is! [center][u][b]FEATURES:[/b][/u][/center] -Vote4Cash -Webclient Ready -Clipped NPC following -Clipped Following -Skilling area (hadn't time to change it) -Unique home -Unqiue shops -Hunter -Farming -Fishing -Allot of NPC's (NO LAGG) -Fully working Cwars -Several Minigames -Awesome PvP -Awesome PvM -Report System -ALLOT more
[center][u][b]MEDIA[/b][/u][/center] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2yzbpj4.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2462zio.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/2yw6bnn.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/4pttn6.jpg[/img] (sorry for white stuff around it)
Source Link: http://up.ht/OP2tqh
Client Link: http://up.ht/R5m22r
Files that fix the errors: http://www.mediafire.com/?v0j4jyqnytrgkrb
Credits: -me -I_Hybrid_I for helping me in difficult times and working on source :) -Genesis (for making the awesome base!) -Proxx for being awesome/programming the source
